~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- `ZedBoard <https://digilent.com/reference/programmable-logic/zedboard/start>`__
  Rev C or later
- :adi:`{{ eval_board }}` FMC board
- SD card with at least 16GB of memory
- Micro-USB cable
- Ethernet cable
