Necessary files
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

The following files are needed for the system to boot:

- HDL boot file: ``system_top.xsa``
- no-OS project: :git-no-os:`{{ no_os_project_path }}`

