  will include Vivado as well)
- An UART terminal (Putty/Tera Term/Minicom, etc.), Baud rate 115200 (8N1)

Required hardware
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

